<br>
You may need to set graphics detail settings to high to see all of it.<br>
<br>
Tinkers can now make a variety of fireworks other than the happy panda - they can make Angry Bee, Blazing Comet, Ground Blossom, Happy dragon (20 charge original firework graphic),etc. Ground Blossom - this one has to be seen to be believed...  Fiery explosion, then a red column of flame, culminating with 4 streamers of fire (like thousands of fire bolts) launching from the air far above the target in lines to the north , south, east and west.<br>
<br>
Grab a tinkerer and have a fire works party  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
